當日有開店；佔領期間幾乎完全沒有生意，在附近工作的客人放工便離開，她曾要求業主減租但不果。<br />\n<br />\n928冇生意唔出奇,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但之後點會冇生意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"典型港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d505fefa90daba2e578e6a414ca8dc121d4fc18","tid":1606263,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"佢老母啦<br />\n唔出黎就後悔啦"},{"pid":"f9bd84acd91fa5f7c95752330ed920204348475a","tid":1606263,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"想正皮俾Wing，負皮俾Emme"}]}